{"id":20,"date":"2024-06-03T15:13:56","date_gmt":"2024-06-03T20:13:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?page_id=20"},"modified":"2024-08-07T21:20:08","modified_gmt":"2024-08-08T02:20:08","slug":"hazing-statistics","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/what-is-hazing\/hazing-statistics\/","title":{"rendered":"Hazing Statistics"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Hazing is more common than most people realize, and no level of hazing is allowed or acceptable.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">National Hazing Statistics<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing is not a challenge unique to any one campus, but is common in sports, clubs and student organizations across the nation.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper ua-util_align--center \"><ul class=\"ua_layout--grid\" style=row-gap:var(--ua_space--flow-double);--grid-column-count:3>\n<li  style = \"align-content: start \">\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight ua_align--left\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">55%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">of those in student orgs. have been hazed<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">91%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">did not realize it<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">95%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">did not report<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">1 in 10<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">labeled it as hazing<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight ua_align--left\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">74%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">of student-athletes experience hazing<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Presence of Alcohol<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Alcohol is often involved in hazing incidents.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><ul class=\"ua_layout--grid\" style=--grid-column-count:3>\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight ua_align--left\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">71%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">of students witnessed alcohol-related hazing<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight ua_align--left\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">47%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">of student-athletes report drinking games<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n\n<li  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight ua_align--left\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">82%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">of hazing deaths are alcohol-related<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Before College<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Many students experience hazing even before college begins.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">1.5 million<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">high school students experience hazing each year<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">47%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">of college students were hazed in high school<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper \">\n      <p class=\"ua_data-highlight\"><strong class=\"ua_data-highlight_stat\">25%<\/strong>\n        <span class=\"ua_data-highlight_description\">are hazed before age 13<\/span>\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sources<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>National data was primarily sourced from the national study Hazing in View: Students at Risk conducted by Elizabeth Allan, Ph.D. and Mary Madden, Ph.D.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hoover and Pollard, 2000<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Allan, E.J. and Madden, M., 2008<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>WITH US Center for Bystander Intervention, 2020<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hazing is more common than most people realize, and no level of hazing is allowed or acceptable. National Hazing Statistics Hazing is not a challenge unique to any one campus, but is common in sports, clubs and student organizations across the nation. Presence of Alcohol Alcohol is often involved in hazing incidents. Before College Many [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":17,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"hero_blocks":"","sidebar_menu":"","sidebar":false,"sidebar_type":"select","hero":false,"title_alignment":"left","title_width":"standard","footnotes":"[]"},"class_list":["post-20","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/20","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"hr